^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, the bidding was fine. The only two reasonable bids by North are 2N showing 12-14 with hearts, or 2C. And I like 2N better, since the clubs are so weak. As to whether peekaboo should bid 1H or 2H. If I have a Weak-2, I tend to bid two. But once there is an opening bid, it becomes more risky, because one of the opponents has already shown a strong hand. So, some people prefer to have a better suit, although not me.|
